{"tid":1513163,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"茶餐廳日日播TVB , 真係要大家幫手轉台","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:18:17.000Z","uid":230703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64b8f6e06f58f44e37bcfc949e627e4f31cdd751","tid":1513163,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:08:07.000Z","msg":"聽日講，好似部部andriod 都可以裝remote, 大家幫下手，係甘轉台，轉99點好， 唔係轉82 台都好呀。<br />\n<br />\nd 叔叔婆婆就係甘，比佢地日日洗腦。"},{"pid":"534490a66c4521c46d7ad8cc78a4471c191ec2bd","tid":1513163,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5P7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=a9b2ef93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5P7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=c0b2ba3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5P7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=37b257fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4ca623ea290ee7eb839f49ec9fe9aba079e86e5d","tid":1513163,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"［安全須知］香城Online懶人包 - 落場前背L曬佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2d7903085f5aa3274ad20990d5a9e719189be53","tid":1513163,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2wVB0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2wVB0Q.jpg&h=4c3e5add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌網頁:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e5%2591%25bd%25e9%2581%258b%25e8%2587%25aa%25e9%2581%25b8%25e9%2581%2599%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2599%25a8%2F&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5P7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=4e8a651c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原post: </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1513167/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1513167/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmfGxzt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmfGxzt.jpg&h=3670f2da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB報導偏頗，不盡不實，屢次抹黑反送中示威活動，出賣香港市民。<br />\n在此呼籲<span style=\"color: red;\">全港18區抗爭者，合力將所有酒樓，茶餐廳，醫院，護老院，健身室等公共空間的電視轉台。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由TVB 81/82/83/84/85 轉去 港台 31/32，開電視 77 或 Viu TV 99台。</span><br />\n<br />\n小弟對萬用遙控略有認識，在過去一個月，與工廠開發了一款<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭專用遙控器</span> (universal remote)。<br />\n<br />\n產品可控制<span style=\"color: red;\">9大電視品牌 + 1個自選品牌</span>，於出廠時已預設轉台及其他基本功能。 簡易操作如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 查看電視品牌<br />\n<br />\n2. 按鍵選擇該品牌<br />\n<br />\n3. 按CH+-鍵轉台<br />\n<br />\n現眾籌HKD120000，當中已包括開發和測試費用，4000件大貨，4%眾籌平台手續費，運輸到全港18區和18區智能櫃費用。</span><br />\n<br />\n如眾籌達標，將隨即下訂單，預計約30天內交貨。<br />\n<br />\n請捐款者screen cap捐款成功畫面，email到freehkremote@gmail.com，告知希望取貨的地區。<br />\n<br />\n當貨到香港，我將以捐款者的email聯絡，告知所屬地區的取貨密碼和地址。<br />\n<br />\n這次眾籌屬個人自發，沒有人手，故只能用<span style=\"color: red;\">honour system，煩請捐$50者自取一件，$100者自取兩件，如此類推。 由於智能櫃有時間限制，請於通知發出後40小時內取貨。 由於無法控制參與者是否全部自律，恕不能保證捐款者一定能取得產品，只能做到盡量安排，先到先得。</span><br />\n<br />\n眾籌目的，不像Kickstarter或Indiegogo買產品，而是要令更多的香港抗爭者加入全港轉台行列。<br />\n<br />\n多謝支持！！<span style=\"color: red;\"> 香港人加油！！</span>"}]}